    <summary>Install the minimum required Qt components.</summary>
    <description>
This package should not typically be installed on its own.
It is intended to be included as a dependency on other packages that actually install Qt components.

Uses the Qt Unified Installer to prepare for the installation of additional Qt packages.
This will install Qt Creator and setup the Qt Maintenance Tool.

Valid options for the installer are:

- `/installDir:install_path` - AVOID SPACES IN THE PATH. Does not need to exist, but should be empty if it does. The entire directory will be removed on uninstall.

Options are passed using the `--params` option during `choco install`:

```powershell
choco install qt-base --params "/installDir:C:\Qt"
```
    </description>

